data.description: Beautiful home in Johnson/Model school district!  Character and charm are two words that describe this home. Loved and well maintained by the same family for 30 years and now its time for them to downsize.  Bring your hobbies because there is plenty of room to have a garden, raise some chickens, have a horse etc. Home features beautiful hardwood floors, family room with fireplace just off of the kitchen, large foyer entrance, sunroom, and a large deck to relax on and enjoy quiet evenings in the country! There is also a workshop/barn/garage with power and an above ground pool! This is a must see, so make your appointment today!
